5 receives for reimbursement from the Ad Valorem Reimbursement Fund is
6 less than the amount of funds claimed for reimbursement by the
7 school district due to insufficiency of funds as provided in Section
8 193 of Title 62 of the Oklahoma Statutes, then the school district’s
9 assessed valuation for the school year that such ad valorem
10 reimbursement is calculated in the State Aid Formula shall be
11 adjusted accordingly.
